title: Floater Acoustic Live At the Wow
description:
Floater&#039;s 9th album, Acoustic Live At The Wow. Performances took place on February 22nd and 23rd of 2008.
This is an 11 track album, with 8 bonus tracks, which I unfortunately do not have for the time being. When I do acquire them, this torrent will be edited to contain them.
